description: Entry for challenge 01 in the 2024 DVS Du Bois Visualization Contest.

title.text: NEGRO POPULATION OF GEORGIA BY COUNTIES.

signals.name: font
signals.description: font to be used throught the chart

signals.name: mapfontSize
signals.description: font size to be used for the map titles

signals.name: mapfontWeight
signals.description: font weight to be used for the map titles

signals.name: legendFontSize
signals.description: font size for the legend labels

signals.name: legendFontWeight
signals.description: font weight for the legend labels

signals.name: legendFontOpacity
signals.description: legend font opacity for the legend labels

signals.name: countyMouseover
signals.description: capture county datums on mouseover to be used to adjust the strokeWidth on the maps

signals.name: focusedCounty
signals.description: capture the datum of the clicked county

signals.name: focusedLegendItem
signals.description: capture the datum of the clicked legend item

on.update: isValid(focusedLegendItem) && isValid(group()) && isValid(group()['datum']) && focusedLegendItem['populationDescription'] === group()['datum']['populationDescription'] ? null : group()['datum']

signals.name: height
signals.description: dynamically adjust the height based on the width

marks.name: background_img
marks.description: background image to make the visual look like the original plate

marks.name: info_icon
marks.description: an icon that displays more information about the visual on hover

tooltip.signal: {title: 'Interaction Instructions', 'County Hover:': 'Hover over a county on one of the maps to see additional details.', 'County Select:': 'Click a county to quickly compare across maps.', 'Legend Select:': 'Click a legend item to filter all counties to a specific population range', 'Clear Selections:': 'Click on the paper background to clear selections.'}

marks.name: legend1_group
marks.description: group for the legend symbols and labels that appear at the top right of the visual

marks.name: legend2_group
marks.description: group for the legend symbols and labels that appear at the by right of the visual

marks.name: footer_group
marks.description: The group of marks located at the bottom of the canvas that provide additional information about the visual

marks.name: footer_prefix_text
marks.description: The labels for each footer item

marks.name: footer_href_text
marks.description: The hyperlinks for each footer item

text: Negro Population of Georgia by County

transform.expr: {title: 'Georgia Negro Population - ' + datum['Change'], 'County:': datum['county'], '1870 Population:': lower(datum['populationDescription1870']), '1880 Population:': lower(datum['populationDescription1880'])}
